.sp 2
A partition group snapshot information inquiry by group name or
group ID, such as:
.sp 2
db.snapshot(0,{GroupName:'data1'})
.sp 2
Returns group called "data1" partition group snapshot
information.
.sp 2
db.snapshot(0,{GroupID:1000})
.sp 2
Partition group snapshot return group ID is "1000" message.
.sp 2
