.sp 2
By "group name + host name + service name" or "group ID + Node
ID" check snapshot information of a node, such as:
.sp 2
db.snapshot(0,{GroupName:'data1',HostName:"vmsvr1-cent-x64-1",svcname:"11820"})
.sp 2
db.snapshot(0,{GroupID:1000,NodeID:1001})
.sp 2
